<!-- The paragraph -->
<p>Women Against Paternity Fraud (WAPF) offers many internship opportunities for energetic, talented, and highly motivated university and graduate students. Our current program is located in Bakersfield, California. If you are interested in learning about different internship positions offered, click on a position to read further.</p>

